Subject: [PATCH 1/3] ARM: dts: imx6: add property in chosen node for kexec
 feature

kexec tool needs linux,stdout-path property when loading the
second kernel. So add it in chosen node.

Signed-off-by: Meng Li <Meng.Li@windriver.com>
---
 arch/arm/boot/dts/imx6qdl-sabresd.dtsi |    1 +
 arch/arm/boot/dts/imx6sx-sdb.dtsi      |    1 +
 2 files changed, 2 insertions(+), 0 deletions(-)

diff --git a/arch/arm/boot/dts/imx6qdl-sabresd.dtsi b/arch/arm/boot/dts/imx6qdl-sabresd.dtsi
index 245277b..abf316b 100644
--- a/arch/arm/boot/dts/imx6qdl-sabresd.dtsi
+++ b/arch/arm/boot/dts/imx6qdl-sabresd.dtsi
@@ -36,6 +36,7 @@
 
 	chosen {
 		stdout-path = &uart1;
+		linux,stdout-path = &uart1;
 	};
 
 	memory {
diff --git a/arch/arm/boot/dts/imx6sx-sdb.dtsi b/arch/arm/boot/dts/imx6sx-sdb.dtsi
index 1fe27aa..8e17746 100644
--- a/arch/arm/boot/dts/imx6sx-sdb.dtsi
+++ b/arch/arm/boot/dts/imx6sx-sdb.dtsi
@@ -18,6 +18,7 @@
 
 	chosen {
 		stdout-path = &uart1;
+		linux,stdout-path = &uart1;
 	};
 
